                            <comment id="15358822" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Fri, 1 Jul 2016 11:26:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, in most cases we can&apos;t force users write ExceptionMappers for CXF-specific Fault in order for them to handle application specific exceptions thrown from their code but wrapped by CXF invokers into Fault.&lt;br/&gt;
However, if the cause is null then indeed the actual Fault should be used&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
